WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:04.730
The main goal of acme is to enable architectural descriptions to be expressed in

00:00:04.730 --> 00:00:08.670
a way that can be used by a variety of tools. That is, it's an interchange

00:00:08.670 --> 00:00:13.030
format. Because of its limited goals, it lacks features found in more elaborate

00:00:13.030 --> 00:00:17.120
architectural description languages. Nevertheless, it should give you a feel for

00:00:17.120 --> 00:00:20.070
the importance of architectural description and the role that

00:00:20.070 --> 00:00:25.010
architectural description language can play in describing these architectures.

